metadata.name: The Harvest
metadata.description:
Серпень (ukr. Serpen' - August) is a period of harvest. In the old times, ukrainians gathered the harvest of wheat with серп (serp) - sickle, and this month is named after it. On August 2022 we gathered the harvest of blood, fire and defeated russian invaders, who came to burn our land. 

This photo was taken in front of a real burned russian tanks.
